<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h2>You're invited to <%= @account.name %></h2>

  <p>Hi there,</p>

  <p><%= @invite.invited_by.email_address %> has invited you to join <strong><%= @account.name %></strong> on CrewControl.</p>

  <p><%= link_to "Accept Invite", @accept_url %></p>

  <p>This invite link expires in 7 days.</p>

  <p>If you didn't expect this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

  <p>— The CrewControl Team</p>
</body>
</html>
